{"tid":2514841,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"尖沙嘴美園大廈現涉變種病毒輸入個案　全座撤離檢疫21日","createTime":"2021-05-03T13:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T14:22:55.000Z","uid":240362,"like":31,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"d044142dfcb46597a0614df3e2acd4332d4cdb37","tid":2514841,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:34:39.000Z","msg":"政府今晚（3日）宣布，尖沙嘴美園大廈出現與變種新型冠狀病毒的輸入確診個案，初步顯示涉及N501Y變種病毒株，因此當局安排全座住戶撤離檢疫21日。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20210503/s00001/1620043216141/%e5%b0%96%e6%b2%99%e5%98%b4%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%92%e5%a4%a7%e5%bb%88%e7%8f%be%e6%b6%89%e8%ae%8a%e7%a8%ae%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e7%97%85%e6%af%92%e8%bc%b8%e5%85%a5%e5%80%8b%e6%a1%88-%e5%85%a8%e5%ba%a7%e6%92%a4%e9%9b%a2%e6%aa%a2%e7%96%ab21%e6%97%a5?web_push=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210503%2Fs00001%2F1620043216141%2F%25e5%25b0%2596%25e6%25b2%2599%25e5%2598%25b4%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%2592%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%25bb%2588%25e7%258f%25be%25e6%25b6%2589%25e8%25ae%258a%25e7%25a8%25ae%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e7%2597%2585%25e6%25af%2592%25e8%25bc%25b8%25e5%2585%25a5%25e5%2580%258b%25e6%25a1%2588-%25e5%2585%25a8%25e5%25ba%25a7%25e6%2592%25a4%25e9%259b%25a2%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e7%2596%25ab21%25e6%2597%25a5%3Fweb_push%3D1&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOFLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=a05d46cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210503%2Fs00001%2F1620043216141%2F%25e5%25b0%2596%25e6%25b2%2599%25e5%2598%25b4%25e7%25be%258e%25e5%259c%2592%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e5%25bb%2588%25e7%258f%25be%25e6%25b6%2589%25e8%25ae%258a%25e7%25a8%25ae%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e7%2597%2585%25e6%25af%2592%25e8%25bc%25b8%25e5%2585%25a5%25e5%2580%258b%25e6%25a1%2588-%25e5%2585%25a8%25e5%25ba%25a7%25e6%2592%25a4%25e9%259b%25a2%25e6%25aa%25a2%25e7%2596%25ab21%25e6%2597%25a5%3Fweb_push%3D1&h=ccf3bfa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20210503/s00001/1620043216141/%e5%b0%96%e6%b2%99%e5%98%b4%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%92%e5%a4%a7%e5%bb%88%e7%8f%be%e6%b6%89%e8%ae%8a%e7%a8%ae%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e7%97%85%e6%af%92%e8%bc%b8%e5%85%a5%e5%80%8b%e6%a1%88-%e5%85%a8%e5%ba%a7%e6%92%a4%e9%9b%a2%e6%aa%a2%e7%96%ab21%e6%97%a5?web_push=1</a>"},{"pid":"75843b063ed72b8228ccb7bc6c54e72001ab3043","tid":2514841,"uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:35:16.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心跟進尖沙咀金巴利道美園大廈2019冠狀病毒病確診個案<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  衞生署衞生防護中心（中心）今日（五月三日）表示，正跟進一宗初步顯示涉及N501Y變種病毒株的2019冠狀病毒病輸入確診個案。鑑於N501Y變種病毒株的傳染性較高，中心認為必須採取審慎的感染控制措施，將相關大廈所有樓層的單位沒有病徵的住戶安排進行強制檢疫，以阻截N501Y變種病毒株擴散的潛在風險。<br />\n <br />\n  該個案為一名28歲女子，為家庭主婦，她於四月四日乘搭由TATA SIA Airlines（Vistara）營運的航班UK6395從印度德里飛抵香港，四月四日至二十五日於富豪東方酒店進行檢疫，四月二十五日完成檢疫後返回尖沙咀金巴利道69-71A號美園大廈住所居住。她於四月二十六日到伊利沙伯醫院求診，於急症室採集的樣本對2019冠狀病毒病病毒檢測結果呈陰性。根據強制檢測要求，她於四月三十日到社區檢測中心進行抵港後第26日的檢測，其結果為「不確定」，她於五月二日獲安排入院接受進一步檢測，病毒檢測結果呈初步陽性，並對2019冠狀病毒病抗體呈陽性。由於該個案在四月二十五日至五月二日於社區逗留期間可能具傳染性，為審慎起見，中心會根據《預防及控制疾病規例》（第599A章），將該大廈所有樓層的單位（約涉及40個單位）沒有病徵的住戶送往檢疫中心；若住戶出現病徵，則會被送往醫院接受治療。該些人士將會進行21天強制檢疫。<br />\n <br />\n  此外，中心亦正繼續跟進早前涉及N501Y變種病毒株的確診本地個案(11643、11672和11773)，隨着個案追蹤辦公室進行了進一步調查，中心發現該三宗個案均曾於四月十一日到訪東涌東薈城，而個案11643和11672於當日曾光顧位於東涌海堤灣畔地下S號舖的食肆Curry Lounge。政府會向曾於四月十一日於該兩個處所逗留的人士（包括訪客和員工）發出強制檢測公告。政府提醒相關人士必須遵從強制檢測公告，接受2019冠狀病毒病核酸檢測。<br />\n <br />\n  中心表示，面對變種病毒株的威脅，接種疫苗已刻不容緩。政府已展開2019冠狀病毒病疫苗接種計劃，中心呼籲市民應盡快接種新冠疫苗，保護自己和保護身邊的人。市民可於疫苗接種計劃專題網站（<a href=\"http://www.covidvaccine.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.covidvaccine.gov.hk&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOFLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=525afede\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.covidvaccine.gov.hk</a>）獲取更多詳情。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2021年5月3日（星期一）<br />\n香港時間21時29分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202105/03/P2021050300791.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202105%2F03%2FP2021050300791.htm&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOFLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=facd5121\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202105/03/P2021050300791.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a50ebf4565f098fc39a216e9a93d17c22ec8bf3b","tid":2514841,"uid":243761,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:35:16.000Z","msg":"又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4745337ff5d64112e6e8f22659327fde36cfe67b","tid":2514841,"uid":173713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:35:46.000Z","msg":"印度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4985c84a5645eb0d7ec53dfd05c11a53ef2d4cf4","tid":2514841,"uid":66049,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:36:05.000Z","msg":"有無咁撚誇張啊"},{"pid":"30205cdcf2b3598ce3aa5abdae3e919b25b3ed14","tid":2514841,"uid":243761,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:36:22.000Z","msg":"抵港一個月先驗到陽性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fb50638fdb45ac9725fc3987b1576fc18e9f309","tid":2514841,"uid":380132,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:36:52.000Z","msg":"永續WFH"},{"pid":"f041c98d704dc1c5764c64d6b1de619c2ea875fc","tid":2514841,"uid":60831,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:37:27.000Z","msg":"又21日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478c1c770c6dceee65e35a2130233af4d63a7994","tid":2514841,"u